---
title: Shrimp, Zucchini and Lemon Linguine with Basil Pesto and Goat Cheese
description: We love zucchini all year long and this dish combines some of our favourite flavours: shrimp, sweet bell peppers, zucchini and basil pesto! A little squeeze of lemon at the end brings the whole dish together.
